-- Minmetals May Sell Axa Insurance Venture Stake to ICBC, Observer Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-19T03:41:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-19/minmetals-may-sell-axa-insurance-venture-stake-to-icbc-observer-reports.html

          
          
             China Minmetals Corp. is in talks to
sell its stake in its Chinese insurance venture with AXA SA to
Industrial & Commercial Bank of China Ltd., the Economic
Observer reported, citing unidentified people familiar with the
discussions.  
 After several rounds of talks, Minmetals, ICBC and the
venture, Axa-Minmetals Assurance Co., are now discussing the
price, the newspaper said. Minmetals holds 49 percent of the
venture, according to the report.  
